The Telegraph - Calcutta (Kolkata) | International | Jolie buys 250,000 ring for Pitt
                                                                                                                           17                                                                                      Jolie buys 250,000 ring for Pitt
                              Mystical band                            
	London, Dec. 17 (PTI): Actress Angelina Jolie has reportedly splashed out 250,000 on an absolutely exquisite engraved ring for partner Brad Pitts 47th birthday.         
	The Tourist star, who raises six children with Pitt, got him the personalised gift, a family wedding band with the names of their children engraved on it, reports the Daily Star.        
	The band has each of their childrens names on it and Angies on the top. This is a family wedding band to symbolise Brad isnt just married to Angelina but to the family as a whole. It was described as absolutely exquisite, said an insider. Jolie, 35, also requested that the band be engraved with mystical references that are personal to the couple.                                                                                                                                                           
